      {{> key-fact fact="Centralize the Queen" description="A queen placed in the center exerts maximum
      influence, controlling multiple ranks, files, and diagonals while supporting both offense and defense
      simultaneously."}}

      {{> key-fact fact="Queen and Knight Harmony" description="Queens coordinate especially well with knights, creating
      powerful attacking combinations, since knights cover unusual squares that complement the queen's wide-ranging
      power."}}

      {{> key-fact fact="Common Checkmating Tool" description="The queen frequently delivers checkmate, especially when
      supported by another piece, using her sweeping range to restrict the king's escape and secure victory."}}
    </div>
  </div>

